cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM

The paper deals with visual recognition and domain adaptation, which are both topics commonly studied in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of kernel regression and parametric spaces also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the mention of lighting and sensor type implies a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM).
